## Decisions and Action Items
* **`draft-irtf-qirg-qi-multiplane-arch`**:
  * The authors will revise the draft to remove or clarify the use of the term "forwarding" in quantum contexts.
  * The authors will work to classify the listed QoS parameters into topology constraints versus per-request constraints.
  * The term "optical transport network (OTN)" will be generalized to "optical networks" to avoid conflicting definitions.
* **`draft-cacciapuoti-qirg-quantum-native-architecture`**:
  * The authors will prepare version -02 to clarify definition boundaries, detail the integration of classical signaling in the quantum data plane, and address feedback from *Rodney Van Meter*.
* **`draft-zhu-qirg-qdcp`**:
  * The authors will consider migrating the protocol definition to support IPv6 and explore extensible TLV structures or high-level serialization mechanisms (e.g., Protocol Buffers) based on group feedback.

